{"tid":1707975,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有鑑於已經有兩人被實彈擊中，我想講少少有關鎗械既基本常識","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:47:09.000Z","uid":18672,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1456cb61658c7f0f820e2035b2f2fc9b60d5572e","tid":1707975,"uid":18672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"1. 準備拔鎗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1no39rg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1no39rg.png&h=913cfa8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruOvPrZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruOvPrZ.jpg&h=0ea33e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果冇明確既口頭警告，應該將此動作視為<span style=\"color: red;\">第一個警告</span><br />\n任何人（即使係受過訓練既專業人士）都唔應該覺得自己有能力阻止其他人拔鎗<br />\n係特殊情況下，由拔鎗到瞄準射擊只需要0.5秒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g11oE_nxWSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg11oE_nxWSU&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B4V%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=c6108af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g11oE_nxWSU</a><br />\n（牛仔射擊比賽）<br />\n<br />\n情況許可既情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">應該慢慢後退，直到有掩護物</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 鎗口指住人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTBUwHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTBUwHH.png&h=5569eccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c41tBbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc41tBbe.png&h=aef91af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當鎗口指住人，如果仍然係冇明確既口頭警告，<span style=\"color: red;\">應該假設射手隨時有可能射擊亦係最後一個警告</span><br />\n電影好多時有特工被人用手鎗指住時搶走該把鎗既場面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家千其唔好模仿</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你不幸被人用鎗指住，<span style=\"color: red;\">請你立即舉高雙手企係原地等射手既指示，只有特殊情況下你應該慢慢後退</span><br />\n如果你見到有人被人用鎗指住，而你就係個個人附近，<span style=\"color: red;\">請你立即舉高雙手慢慢後退</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除此之外，大家亦都應該要時刻留意是否有人做出以上的動作</span></span>"},{"pid":"353e8b1e552cd1253459557aaa1060ad8cabdede","tid":1707975,"uid":18672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"推一推希望有更多小朋友睇到"},{"pid":"cc8f160d7260fb8436e8c0bebc5fb03c0dc1ea76","tid":1707975,"uid":18672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"推一推希望有更多小朋友睇到"},{"pid":"79aa50fa5f4a0d30acc0667ad4b5c58ac381b674","tid":1707975,"uid":288912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅態度，求吓你哋<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"921121241579bbe1135ee94ae91047f25566c6e7","tid":1707975,"uid":40887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed4d415bb02b8026c11b682be35cf1ea932da6d0","tid":1707975,"uid":156149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n冇經過合適既訓練最好唔好試搶鎗"},{"pid":"b402f04d511249925f152f3f69f7368122722c64","tid":1707975,"uid":149257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d24c9b271015b51316b43ccda2c007be09fe75a5","tid":1707975,"uid":111929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:02.000Z","msg":"有用post 推"},{"pid":"81e244cfdb4c5f4189bb56e237b8864665b87815","tid":1707975,"uid":172999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"3daf1e7701a16cb04ead853b162030419b4b8ee8","tid":1707975,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:45:29.000Z","msg":"點只兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493079d055a0dd5690f7580ba4c9d929a3